任天堂开始使用 Nintendo Switch 举办老年人活动https://p2y.jp/nintendo-begins-events-with-nintendo-switch-for-the-elderly/ https://p2y.jp/nintendo-begins-events-with-nintendo-switch-for-the-elderly/#respondp2y_admin Wed, 01 Nov 2023 06:23:16 +0000 ゲーム任天堂Nintendo SwitchNintendo Switch Sportsマリオマリオカート川島隆太脳トレ高齢者https://p2y.jp/?p=104874 <p>任天堂于 2023 年 11 月 1 日（令和 5 年）宣布开始使用 Nintendo Switch 举办针对老年人的活动。该举措旨在在日本境内提供服务[...]</p><a href="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-begins-events-with-nintendo-switch-for-the-elderly/">任天堂开始使用 Nintendo Switch 为老年人举办活动的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>任天堂于 2023 年 11 月 1 日宣布，开始为使用 Nintendo <strong>Switch 的</strong>老年人举办活动。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="860" height="460" data-attachment-id="104877" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/nintendo-begins-events-with-nintendo-switch-for-the-elderly/nintendo_begins_events_with_nintendo_switch_for_the_elderly/" data-orig-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nintendo_begins_events_with_nintendo_switch_for_the_elderly.jpg?fit=860%2C460&amp;ssl=1" data-orig-size="860,460" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="nintendo_begins_events_with_nintendo_switch_for_the_elderly" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nintendo_begins_events_with_nintendo_switch_for_the_elderly.jpg?fit=860%2C460&amp;ssl=1" data-large-file="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nintendo_begins_events_with_nintendo_switch_for_the_elderly.jpg?fit=860%2C460&amp;ssl=1" src="https://i0.wp.com/p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/nintendo_begins_events_with_nintendo_switch_for_the_elderly.jpg?resize=860%2C460&#038;ssl=1" alt="任天堂开始使用 Nintendo Switch 举办老年人活动" class="wp-image-104877" data-recalc-dims="1"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿©任天堂</figcaption></figure><p>该活动将在日本的养老院和老年福利机构举行，老年人将接受由东北大学川岛龙太教授指导的“成人任天堂开关训练大脑训练”和“任天堂开关运动”大学老龄化研究所。通过在员工的支持下创造玩“马里奥赛车8豪华版”等软件的机会，我们的目标是让任天堂 Switch 和该公司的游戏软件比以往任何时候都更广泛的年龄段的人们熟悉.这已经成为一件事了。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ADCreHcV5BthD5R3ygfaTglDPURZivN_MR6TC4kby2ILI0kyl1RqpZrKbv-49w-Gm4FbIoa5ex3s_XUEP9n5hpbaq4H9LzOAVzB-ECXYc52jL63dfpjh28H_ijmYQZIzqUiURPKfxwnQu0antg7HrW-2Sddu=w860-h460-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿©任天堂</figcaption></figure><p></p><div class="yrfus65425cba3064c" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
