ed/#?secret=nHGGahqCnr#?secret=XLWIvBMQEL" data-secret="XLWIvBMQEL" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC1CfXB_kRs3C-zaeTG3oGyg" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">HAACHAMA Ch Haato 赤井</a>/ <a href="https://twitter.com/akaihaato" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">HAACHAMA <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a> / <a href="https://hololive.hololivepro.com/talents/akai-haato/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">下一个是阿凯</a></p><cite>YouTube / X（推特）/ Hololive Production</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp 经营代表“Mr.2（暂定）”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber 信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="aDM7cJLb8L"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-akai-haato-to-return-on-november-1/">VTuber Akai Haato 将于 11 月 1 日回归</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Akai Haato 将于 11 月 1 日回归” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-akai-haato-to-return-on-november-1/embed/#?secret=AJuxrtYuic#?secret=aDM7cJLb8L" data-secret="aDM7cJLb8L" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-akai-haato-to-return-on-november-1/">VTuber Akai 将于 11 月 1 日回归的</a>帖子首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/vtuber-akai-haato-to-return-on-november-1/feed/ 0 104763
